        "text": "Deuteronomy 29:28",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; LXX.). And perhaps the writer here chose the word to remind them that the “provocation” at present prevailing among them was to hatred not to love.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
